title: A Blind Crest and a 3 Story Drop: The Corkscrew at Laguna Seca - MOMO
description: Drivers of the #30 MOMO NGT 991 Porsche GT3 Cup, Henrique Cisneros and Kuba Giermaziak, explain step-by-step what it feels like to take on one of the most difficult turns in racing: Turn 8 AKA The Corkscrew at Mazda Laguna Seca.
tags: Porsche GT3, Laguna Seca, Corkscrew, MOMO, Mazda Raceway Laguna Seca
